    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2003-10-28</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-04-19T19:53:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act to increase the limit of the total of contributions which may be made for hazard mitigation measures for a major disaster from 7.5 to 15 percent of the estimated aggregate amount of grants to be made (less any associated administrative costs) with respect to such disaster.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To amend the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act concerning the use of Federal disaster assistance for hazard mitigation measures.</title>
